(21929,'cars','sensors','disable-vtec-vss-check-p72','en','Disable VTEC VSS Check P72','How to disable 25mph VSS check for VTEC engagement on P72: Author: Speedz Date: 082303 15:59 here\'s where its at in the p72 :) 11FD C5 22 09 : RB 22.','beginner','How to disable 25mph [VSS](/cars/sensors/vss) check for VTEC engagement on P72: Author: Speedz Date: 08-23-03 15:59 here\'s where its at in the p72 :)\n\n- 11FD- `C5` 22 09 : RB 22.1\n- 1200- CB 24 : SJ 1226\n- 1202- `C5` 22 19 : SB 22.1\n- 1205- `C5` F3 `C0` 32 : CMPB F3, #32\n- 1209- CA 1B : JLT 1226\n- 120B- `C5` D9 `C0` 44 : CMPB D9, #44\n- 120F- CD 15 : JGE 1226\n- 1211- 90 9D 7D 54 : LCB A, 547D\n- 1215- CE 03 : JNE 121A\n- 1217- D8 31 0C : JBR off 31.0, 1226\n- 121A- DB 1E 03 : JBR off 1E.3, 1220\n- 121D- ED 19 03 : JBS off 19.5, 1223\n- 1220- E9 31 0B : JBS off 31.1, 122E\n- 1223- E9 27 0F : JBS off 27.1, 1235\n- 1226- `C5` 22 08 : RB 22.0\n- 1229- `C4` 27 0A : RB off 27.2\n- 122C- CB 17 : SJ 1245\n\nlooks like `547Dh` is the spot :) (disable = FF)','cars/sensors/disable-vtec-vss-check-p72/disable-vtec-vss-check-p72.md','2026-06-15 22:15:12',0),
(21930,'cars','sensors','distributors','en','Distributors','A distributor is a device that allows one Ignition Coil to provide spark to more than one (distribute) cylinder.','beginner','A distributor is a device that allows one [Ignition Coil](/cars/ignition/ignition-coil) to provide spark to more than one (distribute) cylinder.','cars/sensors/distributors/distributors.md','2026-06-15 22:15:12',0),
