(22016,'cars','sensors','real-time-programming','en','Real Time Programming','Used for tuning your ECU and making changes to it on the fly. Hardware EasyRTP v1.0 Dave\'s single sided adaptation of Doc\'s original DS1230Y based design.','beginner','Used for tuning your ECU and making changes to it on the fly.\n\n###  Hardware \n\n- [Easy-RTP v1.0](/cars/rom/easy-rtp-v10) - Dave\'s single sided adaptation of Doc\'s original `DS1230Y` based design.\n- [Easy-RTP Installation](/cars/rom/easy-rtp-install) - Hardware mods for installation of the Easy-RtpV1.0 board on an [OBD](/cars/wiring/obd)1 [ECU](/cars/ecu/ecu).\n- [Replacing the M5128 RAM chip](/cars/wiring/replace-m5128) - Replacing the [5128 XRAM](/cars/rom/5128xram) 2K [SRAM](/cars/sensors/sram) chip by a `DS1220` [NVSRAM](/cars/wiring/nvsram) (another [RTP](/cars/sensors/rtp) method, not yet finished)','cars/sensors/real-time-programming/real-time-programming.md','2026-06-15 22:15:12',0),
